ca.utoronto.msrg.padres.broker.controller.db
Class DBConnector

java.lang.Object
  ca.utoronto.msrg.padres.broker.controller.db.DBConnector

public class DBConnector
extends Object

This class provides convenience and flexibility for connecting to different JDBC compliant database without changing the code. The database specific properties and other parameters are specified in a Java properties file. By default, the properties file is named db.properties. The properties files for the following database products are provided.

  • MySQL (Linux and Windows)
  • PostgreSQL (Linux)
Add the logging feature
